item.title: Re: HELP ME!!!!!
item.content:encoded:
Have you tried looking your character up using the Player Lookup feature on BVS? You'll find it underneath the login section of the site.

If that's bad ( it'll be pretty obvious ), make a new character, and send in a Bug Report from there, being sure to include your character name with the report, and that you double- or triple-check everything in there, and add any other information that you feel may help, such as browser and version, etc.
